KKR ‘Actively Looking’ for Opportunities to Invest in Mideast

-- B y   A r i f   S h a r i f
-- 
2011-10-17T05:37:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/kkr-actively-looking-for-opportunities-to-invest-in-mideast.html
KKR & Co., the U.S. buyout firm, is
“actively looking” for opportunities to invest in the  Middle
East , said Alexander Navab, co-head of its North American
private-equity unit.  The Middle East as “very attractive” for deals, he said
at a private equity conference in Dubai today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
